	<h1 class="title">李宇春跨年演唱会唱的那首“二次元神曲”是什么来头？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-04 11:28:12 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20173/medium/20173.jpg?1451875770" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


